name: Selina: Mind at Large
summary: “Selina: Mind at Large attempts one of the most challenging tasks a game can achieve: transporting you into the shoes of a child. That’s because not only are you traveling through the imagination of this young girl in order to save her world, the journey seeks to activate that same sense of wonder, adventure and fear inside yourself as you journey through this storybook tale… you return to feeling like a child yourself, in wonder for the gravity-changing hijinks that ensue, and the personal struggles...
